The paper deals with resource management in a wireless network, which involves information theory (cs.IT) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The problem of designing an incentive-compatible mechanism involves game theory (cs.GT) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The proposed mechanism is dynamic and ensures truthfulness, which involves control and optimization (cs.SY).
